174 A.3d 512 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. RICKEY H. WILLIFORD, A/K/A RICKEY H. WILLIFORD, JR., RICKY H. WILLIFORD, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-165 September Term 2017

079358 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000476-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
